description:
Randy Brecker talks about how he learned to play music and compares the process with Jazzaar Festival's music educational concept 'Bandstand Learning with Role Models'.

Interviewed by: Fritz Renold - Musical Director of Jazzaar Festival
Venue: Jazzaar Lounge 
Filmed and recorded by: Simeon Sigg
